pullRequest.body:
The construction of the adjunction between `nerve` and `SSet.hoFunctor`. As a consequence, we can conclude that `Cat.{u,u}` has colimits.

Co-Authored-By: Emily Riehl <eriehl@jhu.edu> and Pietro Monticone <38562595+pitmonticone@users.noreply.github.com>
